00:15.556 --> 00:19.810
THOSE CUSTOMIZED HIGH-TOPS
MAKE YOU DUNK LIKE LeBRON?

00:19.810 --> 00:21.902
[ LAUGHTER ]
CLEVER MARKETING
HAS CONDITIONED US TO BELIEVE

00:21.902 --> 00:23.644
THAT WE GET WHAT WE PAY FOR.

00:23.644 --> 00:25.646
IN FACT,
RESEARCHERS AT STANFORD

00:25.646 --> 00:28.279
USED AN MRI TO GAUGE
BRAIN ACTIVITY

00:28.279 --> 00:30.701
WHILE PARTICIPANTS SIPPED
SAMPLES OF RED WINE.

00:30.701 --> 00:32.653
GUESS WHAT THEY FOUND.

00:32.653 --> 00:34.865
WHEN PEOPLE THOUGHT THAT
THEY WERE DRINKING $5 MERLOT,

00:34.865 --> 00:37.708
THE MEDIAL
ORBITOFRONTAL CORTEX --

00:37.708 --> 00:39.710
PART OF THE BRAIN INVOLVED
WITH PLEASURE AND REWARD --

00:39.710 --> 00:41.662
WAS MINIMALLY ACTIVE.

00:41.662 --> 00:43.664
BUT WHEN TOLD THAT SAME WINE

00:43.664 --> 00:46.087
WAS A $100 BOTTLE
OF CHÃ¢TEAUNEUF-DU-PAPE,

00:46.087 --> 00:49.720
THE PLEASURE CENTER LIT UP
LIKE THE LAS VEGAS STRIP,

00:49.720 --> 00:54.555
WHICH TELLS US
EVEN THOUGH WE MAY NOT BE SNOBS,

00:54.555 --> 00:59.100
OUR MEDIAL
ORBITOFRONTAL CORTICES ARE.

01:00.441 --> 01:02.022
DOC, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

01:02.022 --> 01:03.854
YOU HAVE AN APPOINTMENT
WITH ROSENTHAL IN HALF AN HOUR.

01:03.854 --> 01:05.065
YOU CAN CANCEL THAT.

01:05.065 --> 01:07.067
I CAN, BUT I WON'T.

01:07.067 --> 01:08.689
LAST WEEK, YOU TOLD ME
NOT TO LET YOU OFF THE HOOK.

01:08.689 --> 01:10.901
I NEVER SAID THAT.
HUH?

01:10.901 --> 01:14.115
Daniel: NO POSTPONING,
NO CANCELING, NO EXCUSES.

01:14.115 --> 01:15.246
I MEAN IT, LEWICKI.

01:15.246 --> 01:18.659
NSA's GOT NOTHING ON ME,
DOC.

01:21.752 --> 01:24.755
IT'S A WASTE OF TIME.
I'M DOING FINE.

01:24.755 --> 01:27.258
Natalie: THAT'S YOUR
DEFENSE MECHANISM TALKING.

01:27.258 --> 01:29.590
YOU'RE COPING, BUT YOU'RE NOT
MAKING ANY PROGRESS.

01:29.590 --> 01:32.263
OF COURSE I AM.
I MANAGE MY DIET.

01:32.263 --> 01:34.014
I-I-I STICK TO MY ROUTINE.

01:34.014 --> 01:36.767
DANIEL.

01:36.767 --> 01:38.389
JUST TO BE CLEAR,

01:38.389 --> 01:40.601
YOU DON'T BELIEVE
YOU NEED TO BE IN THERAPY,

01:40.601 --> 01:43.434
BUT YOUR...HALLUCINATION
DISAGREES?

01:43.434 --> 01:46.647
[ SCOFFS ] THAT'S --
THAT'S OVERSIMPLIFYING.

01:46.647 --> 01:50.361
YOU'VE BEEN COMING TO ME OFF
AND ON FOR, WHAT -- FIVE YEARS?

01:50.361 --> 01:53.194
YOU'RE STILL MORE
COMFORTABLE TALKING TO
NATALIE THAN YOU ARE TO ME.

01:53.194 --> 01:56.867
YOU'RE THE ONE THAT ENCOURAGED
ME TO ENGAGE MY HALLUCINATIONS.
YES.

01:56.867 --> 01:59.660
IT'S BEEN A HELPFUL TECHNIQUE
IN MANAGING YOUR SYMPTOMS.

01:59.660 --> 02:01.001
BUT YOU'RE STAGNATING.

02:01.001 --> 02:04.745
YOU NEED TO ENGAGE
WITH REAL PEOPLE.

02:04.745 --> 02:06.167
I ENGAGE WITH REAL PEOPLE
EVERY DAY --

02:06.167 --> 02:08.459
WITH -- WITH PAUL
AND LEWICKI AND KATE.

02:08.459 --> 02:12.012
THAT'S WORK.
YOU NEED TO SOCIALIZE.

02:12.012 --> 02:14.675
THAT'S WHAT
I KEEP TELLING YOU.

02:14.675 --> 02:16.136
WHAT ARE YOU,
IN CAHOOTS WITH HIM?

02:16.136 --> 02:17.758
ARE YOU -- ARE YOU TWO
GANGING UP ON ME?

02:17.758 --> 02:21.182
TIME.
THIS ISN'T COUPLES COUNSELING.

02:21.182 --> 02:22.473
THIS IS
INDIVIDUAL TREATMENT.

02:24.475 --> 02:26.106
I'D LIKE YOU TO STOP
SPEAKING TO NATALIE.

02:26.106 --> 02:27.318
FINE.
YOU HAVE THE FLOOR.

02:27.318 --> 02:29.690
I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE HEARING ME.

02:29.690 --> 02:31.982
I DON'T MEAN I WANT YOU
TO STOP TALKING TO NATALIE

02:31.982 --> 02:33.824
DURING THE SESSION.

02:33.824 --> 02:36.367
I MEAN I WANT YOU
TO STOP TALKING TO HER PERIOD.

02:38.989 --> 02:42.833
WELL, I-I NEED HER.
IT'S EXACTLY THE OPPOSITE.

02:42.833 --> 02:45.456
YOUR INTIMATE RELATIONSHIP
WITH NATALIE IS PREVENTING YOU

02:45.456 --> 02:48.048
FROM HAVING AN INTIMATE
RELATIONSHIP WITH SOMEBODY REAL.

02:48.048 --> 02:49.670
THAT'S -- WHAT --
WHAT ABOUT MIRANDA?

02:49.670 --> 02:51.672
I MEAN, NATALIE DIDN'T
PREVENT ME FROM -- FROM

02:51.672 --> 02:54.345
FLYING OFF TO PARIS
AND HAVING MY HEART RIPPED OUT.

02:54.345 --> 02:55.676
BECAUSE
THAT DIDN'T WORK OUT,

02:55.676 --> 02:58.299
YOU'RE RETREATING
TO SOMETHING FAMILIAR.

02:58.299 --> 03:01.011
OH, BULLSHIT.
OH, REALLY?

03:01.011 --> 03:02.513
WHAT DID YOU DO
ON SATURDAY NIGHT?

03:02.513 --> 03:07.017
WATCHED "REAL SPORTS"
WITH ME...TWICE.

03:09.810 --> 03:11.572
GET OUT IN THE WORLD,
DANIEL.

03:13.023 --> 03:14.985
HAVE SOME FUN.

03:16.737 --> 03:18.909
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]
[ JAZZ MUSIC PLAYS ]

03:26.036 --> 03:28.038
RIGHT THERE.

03:28.038 --> 03:29.460
COME ON, BUDDY.
YOU GOT TO MINGLE.

03:29.460 --> 03:31.091
DON'T SAY "MINGLE."
I HATE THAT WORD.

03:31.091 --> 03:32.333
MAKES ME THINK
OF BACTERIA.

03:32.333 --> 03:33.924
CAN WE PLEASE
GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE?

03:33.924 --> 03:35.676
WOW.

03:41.972 --> 03:45.185
