03:47.107 --> 03:48.849
I WANT HER.

03:48.849 --> 03:50.441
ALREADY SOLD.

03:50.441 --> 03:53.063
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO STICK
WITH "DOGS PLAYING POKER."

03:53.063 --> 03:55.276
BUT DON'T YOU THINK
SHE'S STUNNING?
I THINK THE PAINTINGS
ARE STUNNING.

03:55.276 --> 03:57.568
I THINK SHE'S A NARCISSIST.
WHERE ARE YOU GETTING THAT?

03:57.568 --> 03:59.990
LOOK AT
HER FACIAL EXPRESSION.

03:59.990 --> 04:02.623
SHE'S COMPLETELY IN LOVE
WITH HERSELF.
I TOTALLY DISAGREE.

04:02.623 --> 04:04.455
De LUCA CLEARLY SAW HER

04:04.455 --> 04:06.577
AS THE EPITOME
OF YOUTHFUL INNOCENCE.

04:06.577 --> 04:08.168
REALLY?

04:08.168 --> 04:11.832
SO WHY IS SHE SO THOUGHTFULLY
ADMIRING HER OWN BREASTS?

04:11.832 --> 04:14.835
WELL, SHE'S CONFUSED
AND SURPRISED

04:14.835 --> 04:18.048
BY HER BURGEONING SEXUALITY,
LIKE THE VIRGIN MARY.

04:18.048 --> 04:20.881
IT'S WHY De LUCA CHOSE THE SAME
SHADE OF ULTRAMARINE BLUE

04:20.881 --> 04:24.885
AS RAPHAEL USED TO PAINT
HIS "MADONNA."

04:24.885 --> 04:28.689
WOW, YOU OBVIOUSLY KNOW
A LOT ABOUT ART.

04:28.689 --> 04:30.601
AND YOU OBVIOUSLY DON'T KNOW
VERY MUCH ABOUT WOMEN.

04:33.944 --> 04:35.696
[ GUITARS SCREECHING ]

04:35.696 --> 04:37.778
[ CROWD GROANING ]

04:42.032 --> 04:43.364
[ CROWD GASPS ]

04:43.364 --> 04:45.706
NICK?

04:45.706 --> 04:47.037
[ SCREECHING CONTINUES ]

04:47.037 --> 04:49.540
TURN THAT VIDEO OFF!

04:50.541 --> 04:52.543
CALL AN AMBULANCE.
SOMEBODY CALL AN AMBULANCE.

04:55.796 --> 04:58.218
COME ON, DANIEL.
I'LL GIVE YOU A RIDE HOME.

04:58.218 --> 05:01.051
NO, I -- YOU -- YOU --
YOU GO AHEAD. I'LL CATCH A CAB.

05:01.051 --> 05:03.684
REALLY? ALL RIGHT.
YEAH.

05:06.186 --> 05:09.600
I'M -- I'M SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

05:11.602 --> 05:15.436
WE WAITED SO LONG TO BE ABLE TO
GET MARRIED, AND NOW...

05:15.436 --> 05:17.738
YOU THINK
HE WAS IN MUCH PAIN?

05:17.738 --> 05:20.571
I THINK HE DIED WHEN HE HIT
HIS HEAD. HE DIDN'T SUFFER.

05:20.571 --> 05:23.824
DID YOU KNOW THAT NICK WAS
A PHOTOSENSITIVE EPILEPTIC?

05:23.824 --> 05:27.998
OF COURSE I KNEW.
SO WHY WOULD YOU BE SHOWING A
VIDEO LIKE THAT IN YOUR GALLERY?

05:27.998 --> 05:30.411
WE WOULDN'T. IT'S BEEN RUNNING
ON A LOOP FOR DAYS.

05:30.411 --> 05:32.663
THERE WASN'T ANY FLASHING
OR STROBING.

05:32.663 --> 05:34.585
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

05:34.585 --> 05:36.587
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

05:36.587 --> 05:39.169
I THINK I JUST
WITNESSED A MURDER.

05:43.263 --> 05:44.725
T-THE VIDEO WAS HACKED.

05:44.725 --> 05:47.017
THAT'S GOT TO QUALIFY
AS SOME KIND OF CYBER CRIME.

05:47.017 --> 05:48.469
SO, WHAT YOU'RE SAYING IS

05:48.469 --> 05:51.311
THAT THE MURDER WEAPON WAS
A DOCUMENTARY FILM?

05:51.311 --> 05:54.775
I KNOW IT'S A LONG WAY TO GO
TO KILL SOMEONE, BUT...
MAYBE IT'S JUST A PRANK.

05:54.775 --> 05:57.688
WELL, PRANK OR NO, THIS GUY,
NICK PERRI, IS DEAD.

05:57.688 --> 05:59.690
WE COULD BE LOOKING AT
INVOLUNTARY MANSLAUGHTER.

05:59.690 --> 06:02.112
BUT EITHER WAY,
IT'S NOT A FEDERAL CASE.

06:02.112 --> 06:04.194
OH, IF I TAKE MY THEORY
TO CHICAGO P.D.,

06:04.194 --> 06:05.616
THEY'LL LAUGH ME
OUT OF THE SQUAD ROOM.

06:08.288 --> 06:10.791
Kate:
THANK YOU FOR MEETING US.

06:10.791 --> 06:13.794
I CAN'T IMAGINE HOW DIFFICULT
THIS MUST BE FOR YOU.

06:13.794 --> 06:15.956
WHO ELSE KNEW ABOUT
YOUR HUSBAND'S CONDITION?

06:15.956 --> 06:19.169
WE HOLD AN ANNUAL FUNDRAISER
FOR EPILEPSY RESEARCH,

06:19.169 --> 06:21.211
SO A-A LOT OF PEOPLE.

06:21.211 --> 06:23.964
NOW, DID NICK HAVE
ANY ENEMIES?

06:23.964 --> 06:28.388
HE, UH, WAS WHAT YOU MIGHT CALL
A, UH, POLARIZING FIGURE.

06:28.388 --> 06:30.811
NEVER AFRAID TO STAND UP
FOR WHAT HE BELIEVED IN,

06:30.811 --> 06:32.973
EVEN IF IT WAS,
UH, UNPOPULAR.

06:32.973 --> 06:34.394
WHAT DID HE BELIEVE IN?

06:34.394 --> 06:37.227
GAY MARRIAGE, OBVIOUSLY.

06:37.227 --> 06:39.650
BUT I GUESS HE --
HE WAS MOST VOCAL

06:39.650 --> 06:42.232
ABOUT, UH,
FREEDOM OF EXPRESSION.

06:42.232 --> 06:44.985
AND HAVE ANY OF YOUR EXHIBITS
BEEN DISRUPTED BEFORE?

06:44.985 --> 06:47.988
THE BORTELL OPENING
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

06:47.988 --> 06:51.411
UH, A GROUP CALLED...
[ SCOFFS ]

06:51.411 --> 06:54.334
...CHICAGOANS FOR DECENCY
PROTESTED IT.

06:54.334 --> 06:55.956
THE COPS BROKE IT UP,
BUT IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT,

06:55.956 --> 06:57.588
ONE OF THE DEMONSTRATORS
CAME BACK

06:57.588 --> 07:00.170
AND TRIED TO SET THE GALLERY
ON FIRE.

07:00.170 --> 07:03.003
IT WAS AFTER THEN
THAT I INSISTED

07:03.003 --> 07:04.424
WE INSTALL
SECURITY CAMERAS.

07:04.424 --> 07:06.256
IF YOU DON'T MIND,

07:06.256 --> 07:08.178
I'D LIKE TO SEE SOME
OF THE FOOTAGE FROM LAST NIGHT.

07:24.064 --> 07:26.697
IT'S DRAFTY IN HERE.

07:28.278 --> 07:30.951
IF YOU WERE REAL, I'D TELL YOU
TO PUT ON SOME CLOTHES.

07:30.951 --> 07:33.373
DO I LOOK FAT TO YOU?
BODY DYSMORPHIA.

07:33.373 --> 07:35.956
UH, Y-YOU REALLY ARE
SELF-ABSORBED.
NO, SILLY.

07:35.956 --> 07:37.578
MY BODY'S JUST FINE.

07:37.578 --> 07:39.630
IT'S THE ONE IN THE MIDDLE
THAT'S OFF.

07:39.630 --> 07:43.343
THE RIGHT LEG IS SO THICK.
IT'S DISGUSTING.

07:46.507 --> 07:48.549
KATE?

07:48.549 --> 07:49.850
KATE!

07:49.850 --> 07:51.972
YEAH?

07:53.724 --> 07:55.355
THIS MIDDLE PAINTING
IS A FAKE.

07:55.355 --> 07:57.227
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

07:57.227 --> 07:58.979
WE HAD THEM ALL AUTHENTICATED
BEFORE THE EXHIBITION WAS HUNG.

07:58.979 --> 08:01.191
OF COURSE.
IT WAS A DISTRACTION.

08:01.191 --> 08:02.863
DANIEL,
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

08:02.863 --> 08:07.197
THIS WASN'T JUST A MURDER.
THIS -- THIS WAS AN ART HEIST.

08:14.164 --> 08:17.167
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU'RE TALKING
ABOUT. THEY ALL LOOK REAL TO ME.

08:17.167 --> 08:18.999
THAT'S 'CAUSE YOUR BRAIN
IS FILLING IN THE GAPS

08:18.999 --> 08:21.211
BASED ON
WHAT YOU EXPECT TO SEE.

08:21.211 --> 08:24.965
BUT UPSIDE DOWN, YOUR BRAIN
DOESN'T RECOGNIZE THE IMAGE

08:24.965 --> 08:30.340
SO IT CAN SPOT THE PROPORTIONS
THAT ARE OFF.

08:30.340 --> 08:32.222
SEE?

08:32.222 --> 08:33.223
OH, MY GOD.

08:36.396 --> 08:40.230
THE THIGH IS BIGGER.
YOU'RE RIGHT.

08:40.230 --> 08:41.852
Kate: SO,
A THIEF PAINTS A FORGERY,

08:41.852 --> 08:43.564
HACKS THE VIDEO
TO INDUCE NICK'S SEIZURE.

08:43.564 --> 08:45.105
AND THEN WHEN
EVERYONE'S DISTRACTED,

08:45.105 --> 08:46.737
HE SWAPS OUT THE FAKE
FOR THE REAL DEAL

08:46.737 --> 08:48.358
AND MAKES OFF
WITH A VALUABLE PAINTING

08:48.358 --> 08:50.360
THAT NO ONE KNOWS
HAS BEEN STOLEN.

08:50.360 --> 08:52.072
SMART, SO LONG AS THE THIEF
DOESN'T WANT TO SELL IT,

08:52.072 --> 08:53.654
SINCE EVERYBODY THINKS
THE REAL "RECLINING MUSE"

08:53.654 --> 08:54.865
IS HERE AT THE GALLERY.

08:54.865 --> 08:56.076
WELL, YOU'D BE SURPRISED
JUST HOW MANY

08:56.076 --> 08:57.417
SHADY DEALERS
AND COLLECTORS

08:57.417 --> 08:59.830
ARE WILLING TO BUY
ON THE BLACK MARKET...

08:59.830 --> 09:03.293
AND APPARENTLY KILL MY HUSBAND
TO GET WHAT THEY WANT.

09:04.464 --> 09:07.257
[ GUITARS SCREECHING ]
Kate: THERE'S OUR THIEF.

09:07.257 --> 09:09.259
WE'LL ENHANCE THE IMAGE,
SEE IF WE CAN GET AN I.D.

09:09.259 --> 09:11.471
COULD WE SEE
THE ALTERED TRIBUTE VIDEO?

09:11.882 --> 09:17.347
UH, IT'S GONE.
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

09:17.347 --> 09:19.269
I'LL HAVE OUR TECH GUYS
TAKE A LOOK.

09:19.269 --> 09:22.683
COMPUTERS WERE NICK'S ARENA,
ALONG WITH BALANCING THE BOOKS

09:22.683 --> 09:26.526
AND DEALING WITH THE...

09:26.526 --> 09:29.820
THE BUYERS. OH, GOD.
WHAT IS IT?

09:29.820 --> 09:31.822
THE GALLERY HAS BEEN
HANGING ON BY A THREAD.

09:31.822 --> 09:34.404
LANDING THE De LUCA SHOW
WAS A-A COUP.

09:34.404 --> 09:36.456
THE SALE OF THE "MUSES" WAS
GONNA GET US OUT OF DEBT.

09:36.456 --> 09:39.660
NOW I HAVE TO TELL THE --
THE BUYERS ONE'S BEEN STOLEN.

09:39.660 --> 09:42.082
HE'S PROBABLY GONNA
CANCEL THE SALE.

09:42.082 --> 09:43.664
MY INVESTMENT'S
IN THE TOILET.

09:43.664 --> 09:46.667
MR. SINGH, ONLY ONE
OF THE PAINTINGS WAS STOLEN.

09:46.667 --> 09:49.509
DOESN'T MATTER.
IT'S A TRIPTYCH.

09:49.509 --> 09:51.171
ONE GOES MISSING --
THAT'S IT.

09:51.171 --> 09:53.213
DIMINISHES THE VALUE
OF THE OTHER TWO.

09:53.213 --> 09:55.515
AND I KNEW I SHOULD HAVE
TAKEN THEM OUT OF THE GALLERY

09:55.515 --> 09:57.217
THE MINUTE I BOUGHT THEM.
SO WHY DIDN'T YOU?

09:57.217 --> 09:59.059
THOSE DAMN GALLERY OWNERS
CONVINCING ME

09:59.059 --> 10:01.061
THAT ART WAS
MEANT TO BE SEEN.

10:01.061 --> 10:03.523
ISN'T IT?
I'D RATHER
PROTECT MY ASSETS.

10:03.523 --> 10:06.356
WELL, YOU MUST GET PLENTY OF
ENJOYMENT OUT OF THEM THAT WAY.

10:06.356 --> 10:09.650
I PAID $800,000
FOR THOSE MUSES,

10:09.650 --> 10:11.401
AND MY ART CONSULTANT SAID

10:11.401 --> 10:13.824
THEY'RE GONNA BE WORTH
$2 MILLION IN 10 YEARS,

10:13.824 --> 10:16.236
SO JUST SPARE ME
YOUR SMUG COMMENTARY, ALL RIGHT?

10:16.236 --> 10:18.328
LOOK, WE ARE DEVELOPING
SEVERAL LEADS.
WAIT -- WAIT. YOU KNOW WHAT?

10:18.328 --> 10:20.330
I BET I KNOW WHO TOOK
MY PAINTING.

10:20.330 --> 10:23.543
WHO?
JOSEPHINE CARSWELL.

10:23.543 --> 10:26.456
THAT DELUSIONAL BITCH
THINKS THE MUSES ARE HERS.

10:26.456 --> 10:28.508
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

10:31.842 --> 10:36.757
WELL...IF IT ISN'T
MY FAVORITE ART CRITIC.

10:36.757 --> 10:38.468
YOU TWO KNOW EACH OTHER?
NO.
YES.

10:38.468 --> 10:41.892
UH, SORT OF.
WE MET LAST NIGHT BRIEFLY.

10:41.892 --> 10:43.353
LONG ENOUGH FOR YOU
TO INSULT ME.

10:43.353 --> 10:44.975
I DIDN'T INSULT YOU.

10:44.975 --> 10:47.397
Muse:
OH, YES, YOU DID.

10:49.770 --> 10:52.362
YOU'RE
"THE RECLINING MUSE."

10:52.362 --> 10:53.984
IN THE FLESH.

10:53.984 --> 10:55.195
[ SCOFFS ]

10:55.195 --> 10:57.037
Josephine:
"MIA AMORUCCIA" --

10:57.037 --> 10:59.659
I-IT MEANS
"MY LITTLE LOVE" --

10:59.659 --> 11:02.703
"FIELDS OF SUNFLOWERS
INSPIRED VAN GOGH.

11:02.703 --> 11:04.955
"MONET WAS MOVED
BY WATER LILIES,

11:04.955 --> 11:07.167
"BUT YOU, JOSEPHINE,
ARE MY MUSE.

11:07.167 --> 11:08.919
"MY WORK CAME ALIVE
WHEN I PAINTED YOU.

11:08.919 --> 11:10.250
"SO DID MY HEART.

11:10.250 --> 11:12.672
"PLEASE ACCEPT
'THE RECLINING MUSES'

11:12.672 --> 11:15.886
"AS A SYMBOL OF OUR LOVE
AND REMEMBER ME ALWAYS.

11:15.886 --> 11:18.058
PER SEMPRE TUO,
VINCENZO."

11:18.058 --> 11:21.641
THERE'S THE PROOF.
THE PAINTINGS ARE MINE.

11:21.641 --> 11:24.855
SO HOW DID THEY WIND UP FOR SALE
IN THE PERRI GALLERY?

11:24.855 --> 11:29.269
VINCENZO AND I HAD 15 WONDERFUL
YEARS TOGETHER IN UMBRIA.

11:29.269 --> 11:31.982
BUT TOWARD THE END,
HE BECAME PARANOID.

11:31.982 --> 11:34.074
HE THOUGHT I'D MET SOMEONE ELSE,
WHICH WAS NONSENSE.

11:34.074 --> 11:38.158
BUT HE LEFT, AND HE TOOK
THE PAINTINGS TO SPITE ME.

11:38.158 --> 11:40.951
THEN YOU READ ABOUT THE EXHIBIT.
THAT MUST HAVE BEEN A SHOCK.

11:40.951 --> 11:43.373
I CALLED THE GALLERY
RIGHT AWAY.

11:43.373 --> 11:46.997
NICK PERRI SAID HE'D ALREADY
SOLD THE MUSES ON CONSIGNMENT

11:46.997 --> 11:49.920
FOR VINCENZO'S NIECE, WHO
APPARENTLY GOT THEM IN THE WILL.

11:49.920 --> 11:53.754
SO I GRABBED THE FIRST FLIGHT
OUT OF ROME

11:53.754 --> 11:54.965
AND HIRED A LAWYER.

11:54.965 --> 11:56.426
DO YOU THINK
YOU HAVE A CASE?

11:56.426 --> 11:58.428
"PER SEMPRE"
MEANS "FOREVER."

11:58.428 --> 12:00.430
THOSE PAINTINGS ARE MINE.

12:00.430 --> 12:03.183
SO YOU THOUGHT YOU'D TAKE
MATTERS INTO YOUR OWN HANDS?

12:05.806 --> 12:08.809
EXCUSE ME?
Daniel: WELL, SHE -- WELL, UM --
DURING THE COMMOTION,

12:08.809 --> 12:11.021
UH, LAST NIGHT, WHEN --
WHEN NICK HAD HIS SEIZURE,

12:11.021 --> 12:13.774
SOMEBODY STOLE
ONE OF THE MUSES.

12:13.774 --> 12:15.816
IT WAS STOLEN?
I'M SORRY. YES.

12:19.860 --> 12:22.783
AND YOU THINK I DID IT?

12:22.783 --> 12:24.785
NO -- NO, I DON'T -- I DON'T
THINK WE'RE SAYING THAT.
A LOT QUICKER AND CHEAPER
THAN A LAWSUIT.

12:24.785 --> 12:27.998
I THINK WE'RE -- WE'RE
JUST FOLLOWING UP ON --
ON SEVERAL LEADS.

12:27.998 --> 12:30.000
MY ATTORNEY SAID
WE WERE GONNA WIN.

12:30.000 --> 12:32.422
I WAS GONNA GET
ALL THREE PAINTINGS LEGALLY.

12:32.422 --> 12:34.374
WHY WOULD I STEAL ONE?

12:36.216 --> 12:39.840
YOU WERE PRETTY QUICK
TO JUMP TO HER DEFENSE.

12:39.840 --> 12:42.262
I JUST DON'T THINK
SHE'S OUR THIEF.

12:42.262 --> 12:45.095
BASED ON WHAT?
GUT FEELING.

12:45.095 --> 12:46.937
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]
WAS IT YOUR GUT OR SOME
OTHER PART OF YOUR ANATOMY?

12:46.937 --> 12:48.558
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

12:48.558 --> 12:50.770
FIRST OF ALL, SHE'S NOT MY TYPE,
AND EVEN IF SHE WERE,

12:50.770 --> 12:52.772
I WOULD NEVER LET THAT CLOUD
MY JUDGMENT.

12:52.772 --> 12:54.354
BUT THE QUESTION
WE SHOULD BE ASKING IS,

12:54.354 --> 12:57.237
WHY DID GRAHAM PERRI
NEVER MENTION THIS LAWSUIT?

12:57.237 --> 12:59.239
I DIDN'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

12:59.239 --> 13:02.662
I MEAN, LIKE I TOLD YOU,
NICK HANDLED THE BUSINESS SIDE.

13:02.662 --> 13:06.076
MR. PERRI, YOU TOLD US THAT
THERE WERE BLACK-MARKET DEALERS

13:06.076 --> 13:08.498
WHO WOULD BE INTERESTED IN
ACQUIRING THE STOLEN PAINTING.

13:08.498 --> 13:10.460
COULD YOU TELL US WHO SOME
OF THOSE INDIVIDUALS MIGHT BE?

13:10.460 --> 13:13.834
UM -- UM,
I WAS SPEAKING THEORETICALLY.

13:13.834 --> 13:17.417
I-I DON'T ASSOCIATE
WITH CRIMINALS.

13:17.417 --> 13:20.420
BUT, THEORETICALLY, IF YOU DID,
YOU'D BE ABLE TO COMMAND

13:20.420 --> 13:23.383
A PRETTY GOOD PRICE FOR ONE
OF "THE RECLINING MUSES," NO?

13:23.383 --> 13:25.515
WHAT ARE YOU IMPLYING?

13:25.515 --> 13:29.139
THAT I ARRANGED AN ELABORATE
HEIST FROM MY OWN GALLERY

13:29.139 --> 13:31.481
AND KILLED MY HUSBAND
IN THE PROCESS?

13:31.481 --> 13:33.273
MAYBE YOU DIDN'T MEAN
FOR HIM TO DIE.

13:33.273 --> 13:35.896
MAYBE IT WAS JUST A DESPERATE
ATTEMPT TO SAVE YOUR GALLERY

13:35.896 --> 13:38.108
WHEN YOU REALIZED
THAT JOSEPHINE'S LAWSUIT

13:38.108 --> 13:40.530
PUT THE SALE OF THE MUSES
IN JEOPARDY.

13:43.073 --> 13:45.285
YOU'RE RIGHT.

13:47.497 --> 13:49.709
NOW THAT NICK IS GONE,

13:49.709 --> 13:53.333
MY FINANCIAL PROBLEMS
ARE OVER...

13:53.333 --> 13:55.956
BUT NOT BECAUSE
I SOLD A PAINTING

13:55.956 --> 13:58.168
ON THE BLACK MARKET.

13:58.168 --> 14:01.801
I'M THE BENEFICIARY OF NICK'S
LIFE-INSURANCE POLICY.

14:01.801 --> 14:05.225
SO HALLELUJAH --
THE GALLERY IS SAVED.

14:05.225 --> 14:08.228
BUT IF YOU DON'T THINK
I'D GIVE UP EVERY PENNY

14:08.228 --> 14:11.561
TO GET MY HUSBAND BACK,
YOU'RE CRAZY.

14:11.561 --> 14:14.234
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

14:14.234 --> 14:16.856
MORETTI.

14:16.856 --> 14:19.479
GREAT.
WE'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

14:19.479 --> 14:23.944
CYBER JUST RECOVERED THE VIDEO
THAT CAUSED THE SEIZURE.

14:23.944 --> 14:25.946
[ GUITARS SCREECHING ]

14:28.909 --> 14:31.912
THIS REMINDS ME
OF WHY I HATE NIGHTCLUBS.

14:31.912 --> 14:33.914
WAIT. WAIT. STOP.
CAN YOU GO BACK?

14:33.914 --> 14:35.205
UH, FRAME BY FRAME?

14:35.205 --> 14:37.667
THERE. RIGHT THERE.

14:37.667 --> 14:39.129
YOU THINK IT MEANS
SOMETHING?

14:39.129 --> 14:40.550
IT'S A SYMBOL
FOR "CHAOS."

14:40.550 --> 14:43.093
LIKE SOME SORT
OF A SIGNATURE?
MAYBE.

14:43.093 --> 14:45.305
MAYBE A CALLING CARD FOR SOME
GROUP PROTESTING THE EXHIBIT.

14:45.305 --> 14:47.427
GRAHAM SAID THEY HAD BEEN
TARGETED BEFORE.

14:47.427 --> 14:49.559
COULD YOU GOOGLE
"SYMBOL FOR CHAOS"

14:49.559 --> 14:51.641
PLUS "PROTEST"
PLUS "ART"?

14:51.641 --> 14:54.724
THERE.
"CHICAGO ART WORLD."

14:54.724 --> 14:56.226
COULD YOU CLICK ON THAT,
PLEASE?

14:56.226 --> 14:59.069
"KAOS HAS MADE WAVES
RECENTLY

14:59.069 --> 15:01.821
"WITH HIS ICONOCLASTIC
VIDEO INSTALLATIONS

15:01.821 --> 15:04.234
"DECRYING
THE CRASS COMMERCIALISM

15:04.234 --> 15:05.986
"OF THE TRADITIONAL
ART SCENE.

15:05.986 --> 15:07.577
"I SAT DOWN WITH KAOS
UNDER THE CONDITION

15:07.577 --> 15:10.830
THAT I KEEP
HIS IDENTITY SECRET."
HMM.

15:10.830 --> 15:15.085
ARTICLE WRITTEN
BY TEDDY BRENNAN.

15:15.085 --> 15:16.916
MY EDITOR TOLD ME
WHAT HAPPENED TO NICK.

15:16.916 --> 15:18.748
SUCH A TERRIBLE LOSS.

15:18.748 --> 15:20.961
MR. PERRI'S SEIZURE
WAS USED

15:20.961 --> 15:23.253
AS A DISTRACTION
FOR AN ART HEIST.

15:23.253 --> 15:25.675
WE BELIEVE THAT KAOS
WAS INVOLVED.

15:27.177 --> 15:29.599
WHAT DOES THAT HAVE TO DO
WITH ME?

15:29.599 --> 15:31.011
WELL, YOU WROTE
AN ARTICLE ON KAOS.

15:31.011 --> 15:33.103
WE NEED YOU TO TELL US
HIS REAL NAME.

15:33.103 --> 15:37.107
IT TOOK ME MONTHS TO LAND
THAT INTERVIEW.

15:37.107 --> 15:40.110
YOU'RE SUGGESTING I BETRAY
HIS CONFIDENCE?

15:40.110 --> 15:43.733
MR. BRENNAN,
KAOS IS A SUSPECT

15:43.733 --> 15:45.565
IN A FEDERAL MURDER
INVESTIGATION.

15:45.565 --> 15:47.407
AND YOU'RE NOT EXACTLY WOODWARD
OR BERNSTEIN.

15:47.407 --> 15:48.778
YOU'RE AN ART CRITIC.

15:48.778 --> 15:50.120
IT'S STILL MY LIVELIHOOD.

15:50.120 --> 15:52.162
IF I TELL YOU,
NO ONE WILL TRUST ME.

15:52.162 --> 15:53.783
I WON'T BE ABLE TO GET
INTERVIEWS.

15:53.783 --> 15:56.456
WELL, IT'LL BE EVEN MORE
DIFFICULT FROM BEHIND BARS.

15:56.456 --> 15:58.288
WE'LL GET A WARRANT.

15:58.288 --> 16:00.790
THEN YOU CAN EITHER TELL A JUDGE
OR GO TO JAIL FOR CONTEMPT.

16:03.383 --> 16:05.005
[ SIGHS ]

16:05.005 --> 16:09.639
OKAY.

16:09.639 --> 16:13.473
BUT YOU DIDN'T HEAR IT
FROM ME.

16:13.473 --> 16:16.646
HIS NAME IS
JARED TENNENBAUM.

16:19.559 --> 16:22.192
WE'RE LOOKING
FOR JARED TENNENBAUM.

16:22.192 --> 16:24.814
YOU FOUND HIM. NEIGHBORS HEARD
GUNSHOTS A COUPLE HOURS AGO.

16:24.814 --> 16:26.816
GIRLFRIEND JUST GOT HOME
FROM WORK. POOR KID.

16:26.816 --> 16:28.028
I DON'T KNOW.

16:28.028 --> 16:30.240
[ SIGHS ]

16:36.326 --> 16:39.669
I DON'T THINK THIS ONE
WASN'T AN ACCIDENT.

16:44.464 --> 16:47.177
Kate: WE BELIEVE
THAT JARED'S DEATH

16:47.177 --> 16:49.089
COULD BE RELATED
TO THE ART HEIST,

16:49.089 --> 16:51.511
SO ANY INFORMATION
YOU CAN GIVE US

16:51.511 --> 16:52.682
MIGHT HELP US CATCH
HIS KILLER.

16:54.594 --> 16:56.186
DID HE HAVE
ANY ENEMIES?

16:56.186 --> 16:57.807
EVERYBODY LOVED HIM.

16:57.807 --> 17:00.850
HE NEVER MADE TROUBLE,
AND HE WORKED ALL THE TIME.

17:00.850 --> 17:04.944
YOUR LANDLORD SAYS YOU
GUYS ARE THREE MONTHS
BEHIND ON THE RENT.

17:04.944 --> 17:08.108
SO?
SO YOU NEEDED THE CASH.

17:08.108 --> 17:10.950
HE HACKED THE VIDEO
SO HE COULD STEAL THE
PAINTING AND SELL IT.

17:10.950 --> 17:13.863
HE HACKED THAT VIDEO 'CAUSE
SOME JERK PAID HIM TO DO IT.

17:13.863 --> 17:16.116
DID THIS JERK
HAVE A NAME?

17:16.116 --> 17:17.707
NEVER TOLD ME.

17:17.707 --> 17:19.209
WAS IT THE SAME GUY

17:19.209 --> 17:21.121
WHO ASKED HIM TO FORGE
THE De LUCA PAINTING?

17:21.121 --> 17:23.793
FORGE A PAINTING?
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

17:23.793 --> 17:25.625
JARED NEVER DID
REPRESENTATIONAL WORK,

17:25.625 --> 17:27.257
NEVER MIND PORTRAITS.

17:27.257 --> 17:28.878
HE THOUGHT
IT WAS JUST A BULLSHIT WAY

17:28.878 --> 17:30.720
TO IMMORTALIZE RICH PEOPLE.

17:30.720 --> 17:33.303
ONE LAST THING --

17:33.303 --> 17:35.385
DO YOU KNOW
WHERE JARED WAS LAST NIGHT?

17:35.385 --> 17:37.597
AT HOME PLAYING Xbox WITH ME.

17:37.597 --> 17:39.439
I CAN SHOW YOU THE TIME STAMPS

17:39.439 --> 17:41.731
ON HIS
"ASSASSIN'S CREED" SCORES.

17:41.731 --> 17:44.144
IF I'D HAVE KNOWN
HE WAS GONNA DIE,

17:44.144 --> 17:46.566
I WOULD HAVE LET HIM WIN.

17:46.566 --> 17:48.318
KAOS COULDN'T HAVE BEEN
THE THIEF

17:48.318 --> 17:49.949
IF HE WAS AT HOME
WITH HIS GIRLFRIEND.

17:49.949 --> 17:52.362
SO WHOEVER HIRED HIM MUST HAVE
STOLEN THE PAINTING.

17:52.362 --> 17:54.244
AND MAYBE FORGED IT,
TOO.

17:54.244 --> 17:56.075
AND THEN KILLED KAOS
TO COVER HIS TRACKS.

17:56.075 --> 17:59.409
SO WE NEED TO FIND THE FORGER.
BUT HOW?

18:06.005 --> 18:07.207
DANIEL?

18:07.207 --> 18:09.839
ARE YOU OKAY?

18:13.173 --> 18:15.014
DANIEL?

18:17.016 --> 18:20.430
ULTRAMARINE BLUE.

18:20.430 --> 18:22.432
WHAT?
De LUCA PAINTED
"THE RECLINING MUSES"

18:22.432 --> 18:25.435
WITH A RARE SHADE OF
BLUE PAINT -- THE SAME
ONE USED BY RAPHAEL.

18:25.435 --> 18:27.937
T-THE FORGER
MUST HAVE USED IT, TOO.

18:27.937 --> 18:31.441
CAN YOU TRACE THAT?
SPECIALTY ART SUPPLIERS, MAYBE?
I'LL MAKE SOME CALLS.

18:36.536 --> 18:39.289
[ LOUNGE MUSIC PLAYS ]

18:42.622 --> 18:44.624
Muse:
YOU PLAY VERY WELL.

18:44.624 --> 18:47.457
THANK YOU.
SEE?

18:47.457 --> 18:49.299
I'M NOT SUCH A NARCISSIST.

18:49.299 --> 18:51.381
I APPRECIATE
OTHER PEOPLE'S TALENT.

18:51.381 --> 18:53.303
WELL,
MAYBE I MISJUDGED YOU.

18:56.386 --> 18:58.137
DANIEL,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

18:58.137 --> 19:00.310
WHAT DOES IT LOOK LIKE I'M
DOING? I'M PLAYING THE PIANO.

19:00.310 --> 19:01.311
FOR A HALF-NAKED
HALLUCINATION?

19:02.892 --> 19:04.314
I THINK SHE'S JEALOUS.

19:04.314 --> 19:06.316
ROSENTHAL WOULD
HAVE A FIELD DAY WITH THIS.

19:06.316 --> 19:10.149
TO HELL WITH ROSENTHAL.
I'M ENJOYING MYSELF.

19:10.149 --> 19:13.072
JUST LIKE YOU DID WITH ME
IN COLLEGE.

19:13.072 --> 19:16.236
[ PLAYING STOPS ]
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

19:16.236 --> 19:19.449
YOU WERE SCARED TO STRIKE UP
A CONVERSATION WITH CAROLINE,

19:19.449 --> 19:23.082
SO YOU CAME HOME AND STARTED AN
IMAGINARY RELATIONSHIP WITH ME.

19:23.082 --> 19:25.835
WELL, IT WORKED OUT
PRETTY WELL.
DANIEL, DON'T MAKE
THE SAME MISTAKE TWICE.

19:25.835 --> 19:27.247
LOOK, THE REAL JOSEPHINE
HAS MADE IT CLEAR

19:27.247 --> 19:29.088
SHE DOESN'T LIKE ME
VERY MUCH.

19:29.088 --> 19:31.841
YOU GOT OFF ON THE WRONG FOOT.
GO APOLOGIZE.

19:31.841 --> 19:34.424
EVEN IF I WANTED TO, SHE'S
A SUSPECT IN AN INVESTIGATION.

19:34.424 --> 19:36.426
YOU DON'T BELIEVE THAT
SHE HAS ANYTHING TO DO WITH IT.

19:36.426 --> 19:39.349
DON'T BE
SUCH A BOY SCOUT.

19:39.349 --> 19:41.180
SHE'S RIGHT.

19:41.180 --> 19:46.015
I'D LOVE TO SEE YOU...
IN THE FLESH.

19:46.015 --> 19:47.607
LEWICKI!

19:47.607 --> 19:51.190
[ SIGHS ]

19:51.190 --> 19:53.523
I NEED A LIFT
TO THE GRAND REGENT.

19:53.523 --> 19:56.276
YOU AGAIN.

19:56.276 --> 19:58.618
HI. UH,
I'M SORRY TO BOTHER YOU.

19:58.618 --> 20:00.029
I KNOW -- I KNOW IT'S LATE.
I JUST --

20:00.029 --> 20:03.243
WHEN WE MET AT THE GALLERY,
I, UM --

20:03.243 --> 20:06.376
I DIDN'T REALIZE
THAT YOU WERE...YOU,

20:06.376 --> 20:08.127
AND I-I-I THINK
I MAY HAVE SAID SOME THINGS

20:08.127 --> 20:12.962
THAT SOUNDED A LITTLE JUDGMENTAL
AND -- AND HARSH AND --

20:12.962 --> 20:14.884
AND VERY PERCEPTIVE.

20:14.884 --> 20:16.386
I'M SORRY?

20:16.386 --> 20:17.717
YOU SAW RIGHT THROUGH ME.

20:19.469 --> 20:22.642
I WAS OBSESSED WITH MYSELF
WHEN I WAS 19.

20:22.642 --> 20:26.396
OH, WELL...
YOUR INTERPRETATION WAS
PRETTY IMPRESSIVE, ACTUALLY.

20:26.396 --> 20:28.728
IT WAS?

20:29.729 --> 20:32.562
OH.

20:32.562 --> 20:33.733
YOU WANT TO COME IN?

20:35.315 --> 20:37.487
HAVE A DRINK?

20:37.487 --> 20:40.740
OH, I-I-I GOT -- SURE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:43.703 --> 20:45.915
Daniel: SO, I GUESS
NEUROSCIENCE TURNED OUT TO BE

20:45.915 --> 20:47.627
A PRETTY GOOD
FALLBACK PLAN.

20:47.627 --> 20:50.039
THOUGH MY FIRST CHOICE WAS TO
PLAY CENTER FIELD FOR THE CUBS.

20:50.039 --> 20:51.541
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]
BUT...

20:51.541 --> 20:54.754
WELL, I WANTED TO BE A --
A PRINCIPAL DANCER

20:54.754 --> 20:56.466
FOR THE CHICAGO BALLET.

20:56.466 --> 20:59.339
I STUDIED
AT THEIR CONSERVATORY.
WHAT HAPPENED?

20:59.339 --> 21:02.682
VINCENZO De LUCA
HAPPENED.

21:02.682 --> 21:04.514
AH. HE CONVINCED YOU

21:04.514 --> 21:07.266
TO TRADE IN YOUR BALLET TIGHTS
FOR A BEDSHEET?

21:07.266 --> 21:08.388
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH.

21:08.388 --> 21:10.390
YEAH, HE WAS
PRETTY PERSUASIVE

21:10.390 --> 21:13.693
AND HANDSOME...
AND PASSIONATE.

21:13.693 --> 21:15.315
HAD AN ITALIAN ACCENT.
AH, IT DIDN'T HURT.

21:15.315 --> 21:19.739
I WAS DATING ANOTHER ART STUDENT
AT THE TIME. POOR GUY.

21:19.739 --> 21:23.072
SUGGESTED I, UH --
I COULD MAKE SOME EXTRA MONEY

21:23.072 --> 21:25.535
BY MODELING
FOR PAINTING CLASSES,

21:25.535 --> 21:28.748
WHICH WAS A BIG MISTAKE FOR HIM,
'CAUSE ONE DAY,

21:28.748 --> 21:31.371
VINCENZO WALKS INTO THE STUDIO,
TAKES ONE LOOK AT ME,

21:31.371 --> 21:33.833
AND TELLS ME
I'M HIS MUSE.

21:33.833 --> 21:35.375
NEXT THING YOU KNOW,

21:35.375 --> 21:37.877
WE'RE RUNNING OFF TO ITALY
TOGETHER.

21:37.877 --> 21:40.510
HMM.

21:40.510 --> 21:43.343
YOU EVER DO ANYTHING
THAT CRAZY?

21:43.343 --> 21:46.926
EVERY DAY OF MY LIFE.

22:03.613 --> 22:07.827
DANIEL PIERCE, DO I DETECT
A TWINKLE IN YOUR EYE?

22:07.827 --> 22:09.248
I DON'T TWINKLE, PAUL.

22:09.248 --> 22:10.870
THEN WHAT YOUNG MAX TOLD ME
ISN'T TRUE?

22:10.870 --> 22:12.872
WHAT, EXACTLY,
DID YOUNG MAX TELL YOU?

22:12.872 --> 22:15.294
OH, JUST THAT I DROVE YOU
TO THE GRAND REGENT HOTEL,

22:15.294 --> 22:16.916
AND YOU SAID
YOU'D BE RIGHT BACK,

22:16.916 --> 22:19.759
AND THEN I WAITED FOR YOU
TO COME OUT UNTIL 6:00 A.M.

22:19.759 --> 22:21.381
I DEMAND DETAILS.

22:21.381 --> 22:23.803
I AM NOT GONNA BE FODDER
FOR YOUR WATER-COOLER GOSSIP.

22:23.803 --> 22:25.675
AND YOU ARE FIRED.

22:25.675 --> 22:27.637
WHATEVER YOU SAY,
DOC.

22:27.637 --> 22:30.850
O-OKAY, SO YOU DON'T
WANT TO SHARE? FINE.

22:30.850 --> 22:33.473
I'M JUST GLAD YOU'RE GETTING
OUT THERE AGAIN.

22:33.473 --> 22:35.104
MIRANDA WAS A REAL PUNCH
IN THE GUT.

22:35.104 --> 22:36.606
AH,
MIRANDA WAS A MISTAKE.

22:36.606 --> 22:38.237
I WAS TRYING TO REKINDLE
SOMETHING FROM 20 YEARS AGO.

22:38.237 --> 22:40.239
THIS IS...NEW.
THIS IS EXCITING.

22:40.239 --> 22:42.151
WELL, WHO IS SHE?

22:42.151 --> 22:44.654
IT'S THE WOMAN FROM THE GALLERY
THE OTHER NIGHT.
WHAT WOMAN?

22:44.654 --> 22:47.487
I WAS JUST --
UH, JUST TELLING PAUL

22:47.487 --> 22:49.489
THAT SHE TURNED OUT TO BE

22:49.489 --> 22:51.330
THE -- THE MODEL
FROM THE PAINTINGS.

22:51.330 --> 22:53.162
OH, WELL,
SPEAKING OF THE PAINTINGS,

22:53.162 --> 22:55.415
YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT THE ULTRAMARINE BLUE.

22:55.415 --> 22:56.756
ONLY ONE PLACE IN TOWN
SELLS IT,

22:56.756 --> 22:59.709
AND ONE GUY BOUGHT
ALL THEY HAD.

23:01.711 --> 23:03.132
Kate: I'M LOOKING FOR
MARTIN GRANT.

23:03.132 --> 23:06.506
HE, UM -- HE DOESN'T
LIVE HERE ANYMORE.

23:06.506 --> 23:08.347
DO YOU KNOW WHERE
WE MIGHT BE ABLE TO FIND HIM?

23:08.347 --> 23:10.770
HE MOVED INTO SOME DUMP AT
THE CORNER OF HALSTED AND 19th.

23:10.770 --> 23:13.012
HE SAID
THE LIGHT WAS PERFECT.

23:13.012 --> 23:16.646
IS HE A PAINTER?
EVERYTHING'S FINE FOR 20 YEARS,
AND THEN OUT OF THE BLUE,

23:16.646 --> 23:19.278
HE QUITS HIS JOB
AT THE EXCHANGE TO MAKE ART.

23:19.278 --> 23:22.111
HE STOPPED TALKING TO ME,
IGNORED THE KIDS.

23:22.111 --> 23:24.153
AND THEN ONE DAY,
HE WAS GONE.

23:24.153 --> 23:25.525
WE CAN'T PAY OUR BILLS,

23:25.525 --> 23:27.527
SO THE BANK FORECLOSED
A MONTH AGO.

23:27.527 --> 23:30.239
IS YOUR HUSBAND AWARE THAT
YOU'RE IN FINANCIAL TROUBLE?

23:30.239 --> 23:31.831
I'VE LEFT HIM
DOZENS OF MESSAGES.

23:31.831 --> 23:34.033
WHEN YOU SEE HIM,
TELL HIM HE SHOULD KEEP A ROOF

23:34.033 --> 23:37.206
OVER HIS KIDS' HEADS INSTEAD OF
DOING ARTS AND CRAFTS.

23:37.206 --> 23:38.838
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

23:42.301 --> 23:44.383
SPECIAL AGENT KATE MORETTI,
FBI.

23:44.383 --> 23:45.755
YOU MARTIN GRANT?

23:49.849 --> 23:53.262
SIR?
ARE YOU MARTIN GRANT?

24:02.562 --> 24:04.403
Kate: WE CHECKED EVERY PAINTING
IN YOUR STUDIO.

24:04.403 --> 24:06.325
WE DIDN'T
FIND THE ORIGINAL.

24:07.987 --> 24:10.409
WHAT DID YOU DO
WITH "THE RECLINING MUSE"?
CAN I GO?

24:10.409 --> 24:13.372
NO. YOU FORGED A PAINTING THAT
WAS USED IN A FEDERAL CRIME.

24:13.372 --> 24:15.495
THAT CRIME LED
TO TWO MURDERS.

24:19.749 --> 24:22.421
YEAH, THAT'S MINE.

24:22.421 --> 24:25.384
OKAY. LET'S START
AT THE BEGINNING.

24:25.384 --> 24:28.798
WHY DID YOU FORGE
THE PAINTING?

24:28.798 --> 24:31.090
THE GUY WANTED IT.

24:31.090 --> 24:33.513
WHAT GUY?
THE GUY.

24:33.513 --> 24:36.305
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO DO
BETTER THAN THAT. I NEED A NAME.

24:36.305 --> 24:38.437
HEY!

24:38.437 --> 24:40.359
[ KNOCK ON WINDOW ]

24:48.778 --> 24:50.950
I THINK HE HAS
FRONTOTEMPORAL DEMENTIA.

24:50.950 --> 24:52.702
IT'S A NEURODEGENERATIVE
CONDITION,

24:52.702 --> 24:55.454
AND IT WOULD CERTAINLY EXPLAIN
HIS SOCIAL DISINHIBITION.

24:55.454 --> 24:57.456
YOU'RE GETTING ALL THAT
FROM HIM TRYING TO COP A FEEL?

24:57.456 --> 25:00.079
FOR SOME PEOPLE, THE
DISINHIBITION UNMASKS CREATIVITY

25:00.079 --> 25:01.921
THAT --
THAT WAS PREVIOUSLY STUNTED,

25:01.921 --> 25:04.173
WHICH WOULD ACCOUNT FOR
HIS SUDDEN ARTISTIC ABILITY

25:04.173 --> 25:05.585
AND HIS COMPULSION TO PAINT,
BUT IF I'M RIGHT,

25:05.585 --> 25:08.427
HE COULDN'T POSSIBLY BE
THE THIEF OR THE KILLER.

25:08.427 --> 25:10.259
I MEAN, HE WOULDN'T HAVE
THE COGNITIVE CAPACITY

25:10.259 --> 25:12.431
TO PULL OFF SOMETHING
SO INTRICATE.

25:12.431 --> 25:13.763
WELL,
THAT'S A GREAT THEORY.

25:13.763 --> 25:16.515
OR MAYBE HE'S JUST
A BELLIGERENT PERVERT.

25:16.515 --> 25:19.138
[ SIGHS ]

25:23.643 --> 25:27.987
ATROPHY OF THE FRONTAL
AND TEMPORAL LOBES CONFIRMS FTD.

25:27.987 --> 25:29.989
SO, WHAT --
HE'S NOT OUR MASTERMIND?

25:29.989 --> 25:31.991
NO, THE DISEASE
HAS PROGRESSED TO THE POINT

25:31.991 --> 25:33.653
WHERE HIS -- HIS MIND IS STUCK
ON A LOOP.

25:33.653 --> 25:35.655
ALL HE CARES ABOUT IS PAINTING
"THE RECLINING MUSE."

25:35.655 --> 25:37.867
BUT HE CAN'T REMEMBER
WHO ASKED HIM TO PAINT
IT IN THE FIRST PLACE?

25:37.867 --> 25:40.329
THAT OR HE HAS PRIMARY
PROGRESSIVE APHASIA...

25:40.329 --> 25:43.542
EITHER THE NONFLUENT VERSION
OR SEMANTIC DEMENTIA.

25:43.542 --> 25:46.215
MY MONEY'S ON THE LATTER.
IN ENGLISH, PLEASE.

25:46.215 --> 25:48.217
WORDS BEGIN TO HAVE LESS
AND LESS MEANING, CAUSING --

25:48.217 --> 25:50.219
CAUSING THE PERSON TO USE
BROAD TERMS

25:50.219 --> 25:51.841
LIKE "ANIMAL"
WHEN HE MEANS "CAT"

25:51.841 --> 25:53.552
OR -- OR "FRUIT"
WHEN HE MEANS "PEAR."

25:53.552 --> 25:56.055
OR "GUY" WHEN HE MEANS
A PARTICULAR PERSON?
EXACTLY.

25:56.055 --> 25:59.558
BUT I MIGHT BE ABLE TO GET HIM
TO BE MORE SPECIFIC.

26:01.180 --> 26:04.523
CAN -- CAN YOU PLAY MUSIC
ON THAT THING?
YEAH. WHY?

26:04.523 --> 26:07.236
IT MIGHT HELP HIM FOCUS.

26:07.236 --> 26:08.898
[ MAURICE RAVEL'S
"BOLERO" PLAYS ]

26:08.898 --> 26:10.529
Daniel: MARTIN, I KNOW
YOU'VE BEEN HAVING A HARD TIME

26:10.529 --> 26:12.361
WITH YOUR MEMORY,
BUT I NEED YOUR HELP.

26:12.361 --> 26:16.786
CAN YOU TELL ME WHO ASKED YOU
TO FORGE "THE RECLINING MUSE"?

26:20.039 --> 26:22.541
YOU LIKE THE MUSIC?

26:24.083 --> 26:26.085
IT'S CALLED "BOLERO"
BY MAURICE RAVEL.

26:26.085 --> 26:27.506
HE HAD FTD, TOO.

26:30.760 --> 26:32.171
DID HE DIE?

26:32.171 --> 26:34.634
YES,
BUT WHEN HE WAS VERY SICK,

26:34.634 --> 26:37.596
HE COMPOSED
THIS MASTERPIECE.

26:37.596 --> 26:41.981
HE HAD AN INCREDIBLY CREATIVE
AND PRODUCTIVE PERIOD.

26:41.981 --> 26:43.482
YOU CAN, TOO.

26:43.482 --> 26:46.726
[ MUSIC CONTINUES ]

26:46.726 --> 26:49.358
DO YOU REMEMBER ANYTHING

26:49.358 --> 26:52.571
ABOUT THE GUY WHO WANTED YOU
TO FORGE THE PAINTING?

26:52.571 --> 26:54.193
ANYTHING AT ALL?

26:54.193 --> 26:57.036
CAN YOU THINK OF HIS NAME
OR -- OR THE WAY HE LOOKED?

26:57.036 --> 26:58.497
MARTIN?

26:58.497 --> 27:02.291
PLEASE? ANY DETAIL AT ALL.
WAS HE FAT?

27:02.291 --> 27:06.045
WAS HE THIN?
WAS HE -- WAS HE --

27:16.135 --> 27:17.426
TELL ME ABOUT MARTIN GRANT.

27:17.426 --> 27:19.849
Teddy:
NEVER HEARD OF HIM.

27:19.849 --> 27:21.721
REALLY?
WELL, HE SURE KNOWS YOU --

27:21.721 --> 27:26.225
EVERY DETAIL OF YOUR FACE,
IN FACT.

27:26.225 --> 27:29.108
YOU HIRED HIM TO FORGE
"THE RECLINING MUSE."

27:29.108 --> 27:31.570
YOU MASTERMINDED
THE ART HEIST.

27:31.570 --> 27:32.772
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

27:32.772 --> 27:35.194
YOU KNEW ABOUT
NICK'S EPILEPSY

27:35.194 --> 27:37.737
SO YOU HIRED KAOS
TO MAKE THE VIDEO.

27:37.737 --> 27:39.538
THEN, WHEN EVERYONE WAS
DISTRACTED BY HIS SEIZURE,

27:39.538 --> 27:42.742
YOU SWAPPED THE PAINTING
WITH THE FORGERY.

27:42.742 --> 27:44.874
THEN YOU KILLED KAOS
TO COVER YOUR TRACKS.

27:44.874 --> 27:49.749
THAT IS TWO COUNTS OF FELONY
MURDER -- LIFE WITHOUT PAROLE --

27:49.749 --> 27:54.383
UNLESS, OF COURSE, YOU DIDN'T
INTEND FOR NICK TO DIE.

27:54.383 --> 27:56.295
THEN MAYBE YOU COULD
GET OUT OF PRISON

27:56.295 --> 27:58.387
WHILE YOU STILL HAVE
A FEW GOOD YEARS LEFT.

28:01.891 --> 28:05.304
NICK'S DEATH WAS AN ACCIDENT.
I SWEAR.

28:08.477 --> 28:10.069
START AT THE BEGINNING.

28:12.191 --> 28:15.194
I MET MARTIN AT A MUSEUM.

28:15.194 --> 28:17.947
HE WAS COPYING
A REMBRANDT PORTRAIT.

28:17.947 --> 28:19.198
IT WAS FLAWLESS.

28:19.198 --> 28:21.410
SO YOU KNEW HE COULD FORGE
A De LUCA?

28:21.410 --> 28:23.823
I SHOWED HIM
"THE RECLINING MUSE."

28:23.823 --> 28:25.584
HE FIXATED ON IT
RIGHT AWAY.

28:25.584 --> 28:27.086
IT DIDN'T TAKE
MUCH CONVINCING.

28:27.086 --> 28:30.089
HOW DID YOU ROPE KAOS
INTO YOUR GRAND PLAN?

28:30.089 --> 28:32.331
I KNEW HE WAS BROKE.

28:32.331 --> 28:36.005
HE AGREED TO HACK THE VIDEO
FOR A FEW HUNDRED BUCKS.

28:36.005 --> 28:37.176
[ GUITARS SCREECHING ]

28:45.684 --> 28:47.306
NO ONE SAW ME TAKE
THE PAINTING.

28:47.306 --> 28:50.109
SOMEBODY CALL AN AMBULANCE.

28:50.109 --> 28:52.191
I THOUGHT I HAD
THE PERFECT PLAN.

28:52.191 --> 28:55.024
I NEVER THOUGHT THE SEIZURE
WOULD KILL NICK.

28:55.024 --> 28:56.856
BUT THEN YOU PUT
THREE ROUNDS IN KAOS.

28:56.856 --> 28:58.948
WHAT, ARE YOU GONNA TELL ME
THAT THAT WAS AN ACCIDENT, TOO?

28:58.948 --> 29:03.783
KAOS HEARD ABOUT NICK'S DEATH
ON TWITTER AND PANICKED.

29:03.783 --> 29:06.956
SO HE HACKED INTO THE GALLERY'S
SYSTEM AND DELETED THE VIDEO?

29:06.956 --> 29:09.038
YES, BUT HE WAS
STILL FREAKING OUT.

29:09.038 --> 29:10.870
HE SAID HE WAS GONNA
TURN HIMSELF IN.

29:10.870 --> 29:13.292
I TRIED TO TELL HIM THAT
EVERYTHING WOULD BE ALL RIGHT,

29:13.292 --> 29:14.713
BUT HE JUST
WOULDN'T LISTEN.

29:14.713 --> 29:16.966
HE KEPT SAYING
HE HAD TO CALL THE POLICE,

29:16.966 --> 29:18.177
TELL THEM WHAT WE DID.

29:18.177 --> 29:20.469
I COULDN'T LET HIM DO THAT.

29:20.469 --> 29:24.223
IT WAS AWFUL,
BUT I HAD NO CHOICE.

29:25.975 --> 29:31.480
SO YOU KILLED TWO PEOPLE
FOR WHAT -- A FEW HUNDRED GRAND?

29:31.480 --> 29:34.814
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

29:34.814 --> 29:36.816
THEN EXPLAIN IT TO ME.

29:38.317 --> 29:43.742
IT WAS MY DREAM...
TO BE A PAINTER.

29:43.742 --> 29:47.166
I WAS GONNA HAVE
THIS BRILLIANT CAREER.

29:47.166 --> 29:49.999
BUT YOU BECAME A CRITIC.
NO WONDER YOU'RE BITTER.

29:49.999 --> 29:52.501
I WORKED MY ASS OFF
AT ART SCHOOL.

29:52.501 --> 29:55.915
AND THEN ONE DAY,
De LUCA WALKS INTO THE STUDIO,

29:55.915 --> 29:59.338
THROWS SOME PAINT
ON A CANVAS, AND...

29:59.338 --> 30:02.551
I SAW
WHAT REAL TALENT WAS,

30:02.551 --> 30:05.764
AND I KNEW
THAT I DIDN'T HAVE IT.

30:05.764 --> 30:08.427
Muse: POOR TEDDY.

30:08.427 --> 30:10.519
THAT'S WHY HE DIDN'T GET
THE GIRL.

30:10.519 --> 30:12.601
WHAT GIRL?

30:12.601 --> 30:16.355
WHAT OTHER GIRL IS THERE?

30:18.107 --> 30:21.110
THERE'S ONE THING
THAT'S BOTHERING ME.

30:21.110 --> 30:23.362
YOU NEVER TOLD US
THAT YOU KNEW De LUCA.

30:23.362 --> 30:25.784
OH, HE KNEW HIM.
HE KNEW HIM.

30:25.784 --> 30:28.287
De LUCA STOLE JOSEPHINE
AWAY FROM YOU.

30:28.287 --> 30:30.539
WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

30:30.539 --> 30:31.871
LET HIM TELL YOU.

30:33.452 --> 30:35.294
SHE BROKE YOUR HEART,
DIDN'T SHE, TEDDY?

30:35.294 --> 30:40.299
THAT MUST HAVE BEEN SO PAINFUL,
SO UNFAIR.

30:40.299 --> 30:41.800
SHE WAS BROKE --

30:41.800 --> 30:45.804
TRYING TO PAY HER WAY
THROUGH BALLET SCHOOL.

30:45.804 --> 30:48.427
I LET HER
MOVE INTO MY APARTMENT.

30:48.427 --> 30:51.060
I GOT HER A JOB MODELING
AT THE STUDIO.

30:51.060 --> 30:52.731
AND THEN ONE DAY
I CAME HOME...

30:54.563 --> 30:57.236
...AND THERE THEY WERE.

31:08.827 --> 31:12.251
SO YOU STOLE
"THE RECLINING MUSE,"

31:12.251 --> 31:13.993
WHAT --
AS SOME KIND OF REVENGE?

31:13.993 --> 31:16.996
NO.
HE STOLE IT FOR LOVE.

31:16.996 --> 31:20.759
ISN'T THAT RIGHT, TEDDY?
YOU STOLE IT FOR HER.

31:22.261 --> 31:24.673
I HEARD ABOUT
JOSEPHINE'S LAWSUIT

31:24.673 --> 31:28.267
AND FOUND OUT SHE WAS IN TOWN,
SO I WENT 'ROUND TO SEE HER.

31:28.267 --> 31:30.509
CAN I HELP YOU?

31:30.509 --> 31:33.272
JOSEPHINE. IT'S ME.

31:33.272 --> 31:34.683
SHE DIDN'T EVEN
REMEMBER ME.

31:34.683 --> 31:36.105
TEDDY BRENNAN.

31:39.108 --> 31:42.111
TEDDY?
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:42.111 --> 31:43.232
WHAT ARE
YOU DOING HERE?

31:43.232 --> 31:45.524
I TOLD HER
HOW SORRY I WAS

31:45.524 --> 31:49.118
TO HEAR ABOUT
VINCENZO PASSING AWAY,

31:49.118 --> 31:50.529
AND THEN I POURED
MY HEART OUT TO HER.

31:50.529 --> 31:52.741
I'VE THOUGHT ABOUT YOU
EVERY SINGLE DAY

31:52.741 --> 31:54.623
SINCE OUR SUMMER
IN BUCKTOWN.

31:54.623 --> 31:57.626
MAYBE THERE'S A SILVER LINING
TO ALL OF THIS --

31:57.626 --> 32:00.459
YOU AND I FINALLY GET OUR TIME
TOGETHER.

32:00.459 --> 32:03.802
TEDDY.
I DON'T THINK SO.

32:03.802 --> 32:05.424
JUST SPEND
SOME TIME WITH ME...

32:05.424 --> 32:08.047
AND YOU'LL REMEMBER
HOW GOOD WE ARE TOGETHER.

32:08.047 --> 32:10.809
TEDDY, STOP THIS.
THIS -- THIS IS CRAZY.

32:10.809 --> 32:14.813
I DIDN'T COME BACK FOR YOU.
I-I CAME BACK FOR THE PAINTINGS.

32:16.815 --> 32:20.059
I TOLD HER
THAT WAS NEVER GONNA HAPPEN.

32:20.059 --> 32:21.900
WHY NOT?

32:21.900 --> 32:25.114
BECAUSE I KNOW RAVI SINGH.
HE'S INFAMOUS ON THE ART SCENE.

32:25.114 --> 32:28.527
I TOLD JOSEPHINE HE'D NEVER
GIVE UP ON THAT PAINTING.

32:28.527 --> 32:31.160
HE'D HIRE
A TEAM OF LAWYERS,

32:31.160 --> 32:33.742
TIE THE THING UP IN COURT
FOR YEARS.

32:33.742 --> 32:36.575
SO, YOU FIGURED IF YOU STOLE
ONE OF THE MUSES FOR HER,

32:36.575 --> 32:37.997
SHE'S BE GRATEFUL
AND TAKE YOU BACK?

32:37.997 --> 32:40.419
SO YOU BROUGHT
THE PAINTING TO HER.

32:40.419 --> 32:45.634
BUT IT DIDN'T WORK.
SHE THOUGHT I WAS CRAZY.

32:45.634 --> 32:48.587
TOLD ME TO TAKE THE PAINTING
AND NEVER COME BACK.

32:48.587 --> 32:50.349
SO WHERE IS IT NOW?

32:50.349 --> 32:54.393
I BURNED IT.

33:00.189 --> 33:02.191
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

33:03.902 --> 33:07.906
DANIEL. HI.
CLOSE THE DOOR.

33:07.906 --> 33:10.659
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME
ABOUT TEDDY BRENNAN?

33:10.659 --> 33:13.242
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT?

33:13.242 --> 33:14.743
HE'S IN CUSTODY
AT THE FBI.

33:14.743 --> 33:16.165
HE JUST CONFESSED
TO STEALING THE PAINTING.

33:16.165 --> 33:18.247
HE SAYS
HE BROUGHT IT TO YOU.

33:18.247 --> 33:20.079
WELL, I-I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE TOLD YOU,

33:20.079 --> 33:22.081
BUT I WOULDN'T BELIEVE
A WORD OF IT.

33:22.081 --> 33:24.293
THAT GUY'S CRAZY.
YEAH. YEAH. I KNOW.

33:24.293 --> 33:26.255
HE BURNED THE DAMN THING.

33:26.255 --> 33:28.467
HE BURNED IT?
ONE OF THE --

33:28.467 --> 33:30.339
ONE OF THE PRECIOUS MUSES
THAT VINCENZO GAVE YOU

33:30.339 --> 33:32.431
ALL THOSE YEARS AGO -- IT'S --
IT'S A PILE OF ASHES NOW.

33:32.431 --> 33:34.263
OH, MY GOD.

33:34.263 --> 33:36.475
BUT, YOU KNOW, THAT --

33:36.475 --> 33:37.896
IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

33:37.896 --> 33:40.309
I MEAN, HE -- HE --
HE LOVED YOU.

33:40.309 --> 33:41.850
HOW --
HOW COULD HE BURN YOU?

33:41.850 --> 33:44.483
MAYBE IT WAS SYMBOLIC.

33:44.483 --> 33:47.106
HE WAS ANGRY WITH ME FOR --
FOR REJECTING HIM.

33:47.106 --> 33:50.109
POSSIBLY. POSSIBLY.
BUT I-I DON'T THINK SO.

33:50.109 --> 33:51.530
I DON'T THINK SO. MAYBE
HE DIDN'T DESTROY IT AT ALL.

33:51.530 --> 33:53.202
YOU KNOW, MAY-- MAY--
MAYBE HE WAS LYING.

33:53.202 --> 33:55.204
YOU THINK HE STILL HAS
THE PAINTING?

33:55.204 --> 33:57.416
WELL, YOU JUST SAID
HE -- HE WAS ANGRY AT
YOU FOR REJECTING HIM.

33:57.416 --> 33:59.418
WERE -- WERE YOU TALKING
ABOUT 20 YEARS AGO...

33:59.418 --> 34:00.869
OR LAST NIGHT?

34:00.869 --> 34:04.963
I-I DON'T KNOW WHAT --

34:04.963 --> 34:08.627
OH, MY GOD.
HE'S PROTECTING YOU.

34:08.627 --> 34:10.089
FROM WHAT?
[ SIGHS ]

34:10.089 --> 34:12.091
COME ON. AGENT --
AGENT MORETTI IS SMART.

34:12.091 --> 34:14.223
SHE'S GONNA -- SHE'S GONNA
FIGURE OUT WHAT I JUST DID.

34:14.223 --> 34:15.554
I MEAN, RIGHT NOW,

34:15.554 --> 34:17.596
SHE'S PROBABLY GIVING TEDDY
A POLYGRAPH.

34:17.596 --> 34:20.439
IF IT SHOWS UP THAT --
THAT HE'S -- THAT HE'S
TELLING THE TRUTH

34:20.439 --> 34:22.641
ABOUT BRINGING YOU THE PAINTING
BUT LYING ABOUT BURNING IT,

34:22.641 --> 34:24.393
SHE'S GONNA SHOW UP HERE
WITH A SEARCH WARRANT.

34:25.484 --> 34:31.150
THERE'S NO WAY I CAN HELP YOU
UNLESS YOU'RE HONEST WITH ME.

34:33.902 --> 34:35.904
OKAY,
TEDDY DID COME HERE.

34:35.904 --> 34:39.248
HE DID TRY AND GIVE ME THE
PAINTING, BUT I DIDN'T TAKE IT.

34:39.248 --> 34:41.460
YEAH, I KNOW, AND YOU DIDN'T
TELL THE FBI, EITHER, OR ME.

34:41.460 --> 34:46.755
WHY?
BECAUSE I JUST -- I-I COULDN'T
DESTROY TEDDY TWICE.

34:46.755 --> 34:48.967
THE POOR GUY WAS --
WAS IN LOVE WITH A GHOST.

34:48.967 --> 34:52.381
HE -- HE -- HE -- CAN YOU
IMAGINE WASTING YOUR ENTIRE LIFE

34:52.381 --> 34:54.343
ON A RELATIONSHIP
THAT ISN'T EVEN REAL?

34:58.927 --> 35:02.351
I CAN IMAGINE BEING SO IN LOVE
WITH A WOMAN LIKE YOU

35:02.351 --> 35:05.434
THAT I'D DO ANYTHING
FOR HER.

35:07.686 --> 35:10.319
BUT I CAN'T IMAGINE TRYING
TO WIN YOU BACK BY BRINGING YOU

35:10.319 --> 35:12.441
A PAINTING THAT WOULD ONLY
REMIND YOU OF SOMEBODY ELSE.

35:12.441 --> 35:14.283
WELL, YOU'RE OBVIOUSLY

35:14.283 --> 35:17.196
A LOT MORE IN TOUCH
WITH REALITY THAN TEDDY.

35:17.196 --> 35:20.118
I WISH THAT WAS TRUE.

35:22.040 --> 35:26.124
IT WAS YOUR IDEA FOR HIM
TO STEAL THE MUSE, WASN'T IT?

35:26.124 --> 35:28.377
NO.
DO YOU NOT UNDERSTAND?

35:28.377 --> 35:31.210
I'M RISKING EVERYTHING
BY BEING HERE.

35:31.210 --> 35:32.631
IF YOU WANT ME
TO HELP YOU,

35:32.631 --> 35:35.384
YOU HAVE TO TELL ME
THE TRUTH -- ALL OF IT.

35:42.471 --> 35:44.313
I TOLD TEDDY
I WASN'T INTERESTED IN HIM.

35:44.313 --> 35:45.894
I JUST WANTED THE MUSES.

35:45.894 --> 35:48.106
HE CONVINCED ME TO LET HIM IN
TO TALK ABOUT IT.

35:48.106 --> 35:49.978
Teddy: JOSEPHINE,
I KNOW RAVI SINGH.

35:49.978 --> 35:53.612
HE'S GOT MILLIONS OF DOLLARS
AND A TEAM OF LAWYERS.

35:53.612 --> 35:56.985
HE WILL BANKRUPT YOU BEFORE YOU
EVER GET ONE OF THOSE PAINTINGS.

35:58.237 --> 35:59.868
IT WAS A COLD DOSE
OF REALITY.

35:59.868 --> 36:04.333
I KNEW HE WAS RIGHT, BUT I
JUST -- I-I COULDN'T LET IT GO.

36:04.333 --> 36:07.996
TEDDY, YOU KNOW EVERYBODY,
LIKE YOU SAID.

36:07.996 --> 36:10.419
THERE MUST BE SOME WAY YOU CAN
HELP ME GET MY PAINTINGS BACK.

36:14.423 --> 36:16.505
Teddy: WELL,
THERE MIGHT BE A WAY

36:16.505 --> 36:19.097
I COULD GET MY HANDS ON
ONE OF THEM.

36:19.097 --> 36:23.602
WOULD YOU DO THAT
FOR ME?

36:23.602 --> 36:28.186
IF I DID...
WOULD YOU GIVE US A CHANCE?

36:30.018 --> 36:32.861
YES.

36:32.861 --> 36:34.613
SO, WHEN HE CAME BACK HERE
LAST NIGHT WITH THE PAINTING

36:34.613 --> 36:37.446
BEFORE I GOT HERE,
DID THE TWO OF YOU, UH...

36:37.446 --> 36:39.368
NO. OF COURSE NOT.

36:39.368 --> 36:41.029
I'M NOT INTERESTED IN HIM,
DANIEL.

36:41.029 --> 36:42.701
SO YOU -- YOU USED HIM.

36:46.785 --> 36:48.627
IT WAS WRONG. I KNOW.

36:48.627 --> 36:51.039
I-I JUST WANTED
MY PAINTING BACK.
AND YOU USED ME, TOO.

36:51.039 --> 36:53.632
YOU -- YOU SLEPT WITH ME
SO THAT I WOULDN'T SUSPECT YOU.

36:53.632 --> 36:55.384
NO, THAT'S NOT TRUE.
DANIEL.

36:56.715 --> 36:59.638
MY FEELINGS FOR YOU
ARE REAL.

36:59.638 --> 37:02.891
THEN WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME
THE TRUTH?

37:02.891 --> 37:05.304
WHAT, DID YOU --
YOU THINK I WOULD TURN YOU IN?

37:05.304 --> 37:08.056
WOULDN'T YOU?

37:10.148 --> 37:13.982
I'M FALLING FOR YOU.
WHY WOULD I DO THAT?

37:17.816 --> 37:19.818
SO WHAT CAN WE DO?

37:22.361 --> 37:23.992
WE CAN LEAVE.

37:23.992 --> 37:26.074
YOU'RE LEAVING, RIGHT?
WE CAN LEAVE TOGETHER.

37:26.074 --> 37:29.328
DANIEL, I-I DON'T
WANT TO PULL YOU INTO THIS.

37:29.328 --> 37:32.501
I'M ALREADY IN IT.

37:41.680 --> 37:44.513
[ SIGHS ]

37:44.513 --> 37:49.017
BUT WE -- WE GOT TO GO.
WE GOT TO GO NOW.

37:49.017 --> 37:51.770
[ CHUCKLES ]
ALL RIGHT.

38:03.031 --> 38:06.865
BEAUTIFUL.

38:08.617 --> 38:11.249
YOU'RE GONNA
LOVE UMBRIA.

38:11.249 --> 38:12.871
THE WAY THE SUN SETS
ON THE HILLS --

38:12.871 --> 38:16.545
IT'S LIKE A DIFFERENT PAINTING
EVERY DAY.

38:16.545 --> 38:18.877
AGENT MORETTI.

38:18.877 --> 38:21.129
THE PAINTING'S
IN THE SUITCASE.

38:24.222 --> 38:28.847
JOSEPHINE CARSWELL,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

38:29.888 --> 38:31.890
YOU SON OF A BITCH.

38:34.433 --> 38:36.064
DANIEL,
I'M SO PROUD OF YOU.

38:36.064 --> 38:39.067
FOR BEING
A GREAT LIAR?

38:39.067 --> 38:42.150
NO. FOR PUTTING YOURSELF
OUT THERE.

38:42.150 --> 38:45.364
YEAH, RIGHT. JUST LIKE
YOU AND ROSENTHAL WANTED.

38:45.364 --> 38:46.995
AND WHAT DID I FIND?

38:46.995 --> 38:49.207
A NARCISSISTIC
MANIPULATOR

38:49.207 --> 38:51.620
WHO GETS MEN TO STEAL
AND KILL FOR HER.

38:51.620 --> 38:52.911
FANTASTIC.

38:52.911 --> 38:55.083
I SEE IT
AS A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE.

38:55.083 --> 38:57.916
YEAH, WELL,
IT'S CERTAINLY EYE-OPENING...

38:57.916 --> 38:59.918
AND NOT JUST
ABOUT JOSEPHINE.

38:59.918 --> 39:02.421
[ SIGHS ]

39:02.421 --> 39:05.013
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

39:06.595 --> 39:10.429
JOSEPHINE IS WRAPPED UP
IN HERSELF.

39:12.471 --> 39:17.105
AND I'M WRAPPED UP IN YOU,
NATALIE.

39:17.105 --> 39:22.320
I GOT TO FIND SOME -- SOME KIND
OF MIDDLE GROUND, YOU KNOW?

39:22.320 --> 39:25.323
AND, UH...

39:25.323 --> 39:30.749
I DON'T THINK I'M CAPABLE
OF THAT WITH YOU IN MY LIFE.

39:30.749 --> 39:34.372
WHAT ARE
YOU TRYING TO TELL ME?

39:34.372 --> 39:37.205
I...

39:39.588 --> 39:42.591
I NEED TO ASK YOU
TO LEAVE.

39:46.094 --> 39:48.927
I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR YOU
TO SAY THAT TO ME

39:48.927 --> 39:51.560
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

39:51.560 --> 39:53.562
YOU HAVE?

39:53.562 --> 39:56.314
I HAVE.

39:57.726 --> 39:59.067
WELL, W-WAIT,
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

39:59.067 --> 40:01.650
THIS --
MAYBE THIS IS A BAD IDEA.

40:01.650 --> 40:05.073
NO. YOU'RE DOING
THE RIGHT THING.

40:12.871 --> 40:17.496
Daniel: WHY ARE BREAKUPS
SO DAMN EXCRUCIATING?

40:17.496 --> 40:20.338
MAYBE BECAUSE
EVERYTHING REMINDS YOU

40:20.338 --> 40:23.752
OF YOUR LOVER
AND HENCE YOUR LOSS.

40:23.752 --> 40:26.254
HEARING YOUR FAVORITE
SMITHS SONG ON THE RADIO,

40:26.254 --> 40:29.888
EATING HOT DOGS
ON THE LOPSIDED PARK BENCH

40:29.888 --> 40:32.511
WHERE THE FIRST
"I LOVE YOUs" WERE SPOKEN.

40:32.511 --> 40:34.933
IT'S NO WONDER
YOU CAN'T GO 24 HOURS

40:34.933 --> 40:36.765
WITHOUT BURSTING INTO TEARS.

40:36.765 --> 40:40.769
WHEN PEOPLE SEE IMAGES
OF THEIR LOVED ONES,

40:40.769 --> 40:42.771
THE CAUDATE NUCLEUS
OF THEIR BASAL GANGLIA

40:42.771 --> 40:44.773
FLOODS WITH DOPAMINE.

40:44.773 --> 40:49.277
NICOTINE AND OTHER DRUGS ALSO
STIMULATE INCREASES IN DOPAMINE

40:49.277 --> 40:52.701
SO THAT WHEN YOU TRY
TO QUIT SMOKING OR SUGAR,

40:52.701 --> 40:56.915
YOUR BRAIN CRAVES
THAT SUBSTANCE THE SAME WAY

40:56.915 --> 41:00.919
IT CRAVES THE PERSON
WHO BROKE YOUR FREAKING HEART.

41:00.919 --> 41:04.713
YOU'LL DO CRAZY,
IDIOTIC THINGS TO GET YOUR FIX.

41:04.713 --> 41:06.545
THAT'S BECAUSE
WHEN YOU'RE IN LOVE,

41:06.545 --> 41:08.046
IT'S NOT AS IF YOU'RE AN ADDICT.

41:09.888 --> 41:13.512
YOU ARE AN ADDICT...LITERALLY.

41:21.940 --> 41:24.152
AND AS WE ALL KNOW...

41:26.314 --> 41:29.908
...GOING COLD TURKEY
IS A BITCH.
